   orbach 's professional career began on the new york stage , both on and off - broadway , where he created roles such as el gallo in the original off - broadway run of the fantasticks ( 1960 ) and became the first performer to sing that show 's standard " try to remember " ; billy flynn in the original chicago ( 1975 - 1977 ) , and julian marsh in the original 42nd street ( 1980 - 1985 ) .

